=== user management ===


useradd username 
passwd username 
id username [ to check the user]
/etc/passwd
/etc/group

=== vim ===


2 modes insret and esc
gg to go the first line
shift g to go to the last line 
yy copy
p paste
dd delete a line 
o to go to insert mode and next line
I instert mode
w save
q quit
q! to quit forcefully
